{"tid":380010,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想買個cam","createTime":"2017-08-29T19:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T23:51:02.000Z","uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2befa2da4c6c037692e146bebb43b56e3466c33","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:28:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n早兩日屋企冇啦啦有鎖匙開門聲，開唔到之後痴左線咁大力拍門<br />\n問過屋企人全部返緊工又冇其他人有我屋企鎖匙<br />\n因為以前都發生過咁既事換埋鎖點知而家又有<br />\n一個人係屋企真係嚇到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想個cam/針孔攝錄機咁既野mon住個門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇平平地既推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n伸利屋村地方走廊冇cam啲看更會亂放人入黎"},{"pid":"f674a63695ff7b7e3458b771596da6d8c4359ac5","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:28:53.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57b8ea6603ce0a1dce75bd1b531570dce726142","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5a6064ef2d63acae50e79f02111a979ba1df5b","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:35:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ae56b28a78d0fa4e53bc74aebe646d82b2949e","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9f128e2853f94a79c08ea6559663d6c6675a30","tid":380010,"uid":118976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:37:22.000Z","msg":"七月節<br />\n有冇地主呀?"},{"pid":"ede2f624417d71deb24adb31ee3ae6a863175401","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:48:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>七月節<br />\n有冇地主呀?</blockquote><br />\n冇呀&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個時五點幾日光日白，我屋企又最近樓梯，應該唔會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心驚"},{"pid":"8f245e9a2272cb6377904afd01e9041941a6728a","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T19:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>七月節<br />\n有冇地主呀?</blockquote><br />\n屋企人係擔心邊個唔記得抆鎖匙比人拎左去配<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知啦屋村好撚多痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然冇乜野偷"},{"pid":"68f187a3aa1d9284810ae4b894ca254b5bd087c6","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c82d6b71bcadaec96003d5d31819fe2741580ca","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd7d551ed00c7e1ca07842d9146ecd658b993e4","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T20:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308b5162044f3a93f2525ac8130e9244c6f65700","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b06cdc76098c4dc3e2e1c0684771334178ec64a","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:27