\n我窮jj係舊式屋村<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(正字唔識打)<br />\n咁得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你有冇問下佢地係咩事"},{"pid":"02230ad2d90e0933bc76bb0b86a74bc90babaf75","tid":380010,"uid":80662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T21:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係住村屋,有時聽到隔離屋朝早同深夜都有,但行出露台就唔見有人拍門(唔係自己個間)</blockquote><br />\n我窮jj係舊式屋村<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/jj.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(正字唔識打)<br />\n咁得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你有冇問下佢地係咩事</blockquote><br />\n冇呀,夜媽媽,d人都訓哂啦,望出去又冇人.唔通開門落樓下睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bfb67fd1109e873523107064484ba924c937d9","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:39:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋邨呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n坊間好多ip cam可以做到啦,<br />\n去鴨療街睇吓啦<br />\n<br />\n但如果影到冇人,你仲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要咁舊既邨，痴線佬多鬼仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nip cam有啦但大大舊，想細粒啲既等佢唔發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n報過驚話冇樣佢都幫我唔到，最多搵多啲人巡我呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151780b387f6dbd8fd704963339fffb007c2344e","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇呀,夜媽媽,d人都訓哂啦,望出去又冇人.唔通開門落樓下睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n怕唔怕係爆格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb17a218d3730130282a6147fe0be3dc1403c916","tid":380010,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>落鴨記行轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唯有係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一聽到咁樣拍人棟門即刻ff佢係痴線佬會拎住把刀係門口等我之後勁驚連行都唔敢行過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b010c460c4d034f2d020c0a13d514ce63f4961","tid":380010,"uid":1979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:51:02.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打試過有鋰電果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔係1星期充一次就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}